00:14:56.326 --> 00:14:58.026 A:middle
workouts indoors at a gym.

00:14:58.026 --> 00:15:00.006 A:middle
And when you use gym equipment,

00:15:00.256 --> 00:15:01.476 A:middle
it has data the Apple Watch

00:15:01.476 --> 00:15:02.726 A:middle
doesn't have and the watch has

00:15:02.726 --> 00:15:04.356 A:middle
data the gym equipment doesn't

00:15:04.356 --> 00:15:04.626 A:middle
have.

00:15:04.766 --> 00:15:06.366 A:middle
So you end up with numbers like

00:15:06.366 --> 00:15:07.586 A:middle
calories and distance that don't

00:15:07.586 --> 00:15:08.156 A:middle
quite match.

00:15:08.656 --> 00:15:10.116 A:middle
