00:15:10.116 --> 00:15:11.446 A:middle
with a great solution to this.

00:15:12.286 --> 00:15:13.496 A:middle
We're enabling for the first

00:15:13.496 --> 00:15:15.316 A:middle
time two-way data exchange in

00:15:15.316 --> 00:15:16.826 A:middle
real-time with gym equipment.

00:15:16.826 --> 00:15:18.666 A:middle
So you'll be able to simply tap

00:15:18.666 --> 00:15:20.376 A:middle
your Apple Watch, on an NFC

00:15:20.376 --> 00:15:21.616 A:middle
reader on the gym equipment.

00:15:21.826 --> 00:15:22.746 A:middle
Your watch will automatically

00:15:22.746 --> 00:15:23.796 A:middle
launch the Workout App and you

00:15:23.796 --> 00:15:24.246 A:middle
can connect.

00:15:24.396 --> 00:15:25.976 A:middle
