00:15:27.266 --> 00:15:27.866 A:middle
equipment.

00:15:27.866 --> 00:15:29.416 A:middle
And data like incline and speed

00:15:29.416 --> 00:15:30.566 A:middle
is sent from the equipment to

00:15:30.566 --> 00:15:31.166 A:middle
your watch.

00:15:31.266 --> 00:15:32.436 A:middle
And when you start and stop the

00:15:32.436 --> 00:15:33.696 A:middle
workout in your gym machine, it

00:15:33.696 --> 00:15:34.706 A:middle
does the same thing on your

00:15:34.706 --> 00:15:35.056 A:middle
watch.

00:15:35.426 --> 00:15:36.446 A:middle
So now, all the information

00:15:36.446 --> 00:15:38.146 A:middle
matches, it's much easier and

00:15:38.146 --> 00:15:39.166 A:middle
it's a lot more accurate.

