These are only a few of the new

00:19:11.476 --> 00:19:12.916 A:middle
features in watchOS 4.

00:19:12.916 --> 00:19:14.306 A:middle
I can't wait for you to try it

00:19:14.306 --> 00:19:14.626 A:middle
out.

00:19:14.836 --> 00:19:16.066 A:middle
Back to Kevin to tell you more.

00:19:17.516 --> 00:19:21.856 A:middle
[ Applause and Cheering ]

00:19:22.356 --> 00:19:23.036 A:middle
&gt;&gt; Terrific job, Vera.

00:19:23.186 --> 00:19:23.696 A:middle
Thank you.

00:19:24.556 --> 00:19:25.816 A:middle
There's a lot more coming in

00:19:25.816 --> 00:19:27.686 A:middle
watchOS 4 including, for

