many calories you're burning

00:20:09.396 --> 00:20:10.436 A:middle
while you're still on the water.

00:20:10.916 --> 00:20:12.186 A:middle
So, lots of new possibilities

00:20:12.186 --> 00:20:12.956 A:middle
here for watchOS.

00:20:13.516 --> 00:20:17.266 A:middle
[ Applause ]

