And there's a free upgrade for

00:20:21.886 --> 00:20:23.426 A:middle
everyone across all watches this

00:20:23.536 --> 00:20:24.016 A:middle
fall.

00:20:24.016 --> 00:20:25.286 A:middle
And that's just some of what's

00:20:25.286 --> 00:20:26.496 A:middle
coming in watchOS 4.

