Now, macOS High Sierra is

00:33:41.176 --> 00:33:43.646 A:middle
available for all of you today

00:33:43.646 --> 00:33:44.686 A:middle
as a developer beta.

00:33:44.686 --> 00:33:46.526 A:middle
And if you sign up at

00:33:46.526 --> 00:33:48.896 A:middle
beta.apple.com, we'll also have

00:33:48.896 --> 00:33:50.816 A:middle
a public beta available later at

00:33:50.816 --> 00:33:52.276 A:middle
this month and, of course, it's

00:33:52.276 --> 00:33:53.906 A:middle
shipping to everyone as a free

00:33:53.906 --> 00:33:56.556 A:middle
upgrade this fall on all systems

00:33:56.646 --> 00:33:57.706 A:middle
that support Sierra.

00:33:58.136 --> 00:34:00.586 A:middle
Now, that's your update on macOS

00:34:00.586 --> 00:34:01.676 A:middle
High Sierra and I'm going to

