And the 27-inch can go all the

00:35:37.176 --> 00:35:38.566 A:middle
way up to 64 gigabytes of

00:35:38.566 --> 00:35:38.936 A:middle
memory.

00:35:39.216 --> 00:35:40.446 A:middle
Both of those are twice what the

00:35:40.446 --> 00:35:41.656 A:middle
previous generation can do.

00:35:42.976 --> 00:35:44.466 A:middle
Now, fast storage has always

00:35:44.516 --> 00:35:45.986 A:middle
been a key part of the iMac.

00:35:45.986 --> 00:35:47.076 A:middle
And so, we're going to now make

00:35:47.076 --> 00:35:49.166 A:middle
our Fusion Drive standard on all

00:35:49.166 --> 00:35:50.276 A:middle
27-inch configs.

