00:58:27.576 --> 00:58:28.646 A:middle
appointment based on something

00:58:28.646 --> 00:58:29.896 A:middle
we've just booked inside of

00:58:29.896 --> 00:58:30.906 A:middle
Safari on the web.

00:58:30.906 --> 00:58:32.936 A:middle
And what Siri learns about you

00:58:32.936 --> 00:58:35.246 A:middle
on device is now kept synced

00:58:35.246 --> 00:58:36.506 A:middle
across all of your devices.

00:58:36.506 --> 00:58:38.566 A:middle
So you're dealing with one Siri

00:58:38.866 --> 00:58:40.316 A:middle
but of course this is kept

00:58:40.316 --> 00:58:41.956 A:middle
completely private, readable

00:58:41.956 --> 00:58:43.446 A:middle
only by you and your devices.

00:58:45.516 --> 00:58:50.156 A:middle
[ Applause ]

