Or even if you don't have

01:09:37.776 --> 01:09:39.346 A:middle
Bluetooth, we're going to use

01:09:39.346 --> 01:09:41.686 A:middle
WiFi Doppler effect to measure

01:09:41.686 --> 01:09:43.016 A:middle
that you're moving in a car.

01:09:43.146 --> 01:09:44.296 A:middle
And when you finish that first

01:09:44.296 --> 01:09:45.326 A:middle
drive, we're going to suggest,

01:09:45.466 --> 01:09:46.866 A:middle
hey how about we activate "Do

01:09:46.866 --> 01:09:48.036 A:middle
Not Disturb While Driving".

01:09:48.396 --> 01:09:50.046 A:middle
And when we do, instead of

01:09:50.046 --> 01:09:51.756 A:middle
seeing all those notifications,

01:09:52.066 --> 01:09:53.396 A:middle
we have this new user interface

01:09:53.396 --> 01:09:53.766 A:middle
for you.

01:09:54.516 --> 01:10:02.946 A:middle
[ Applause ]

01:10:03.446 --> 01:10:04.776 A:middle
Now, if you're tempted and you

01:10:04.936 --> 01:10:06.166 A:middle
try to turn on your phone,

