you're actually going to receive

01:10:07.466 --> 01:10:09.616 A:middle
this, a little reminder that

01:10:09.616 --> 01:10:10.246 A:middle
you're not receiving

01:10:10.246 --> 01:10:11.316 A:middle
notifications while you're

01:10:11.316 --> 01:10:11.676 A:middle
driving.

01:10:11.676 --> 01:10:12.746 A:middle
But, of course, you might be

01:10:12.826 --> 01:10:14.026 A:middle
sitting in the back seat in

01:10:14.296 --> 01:10:15.416 A:middle
which case, you can tell us,

01:10:15.416 --> 01:10:16.606 A:middle
"I'm not driving and you could

01:10:16.606 --> 01:10:17.096 A:middle
get through."

01:10:17.096 --> 01:10:18.346 A:middle
But what if you are driving and

01:10:18.346 --> 01:10:19.496 A:middle
someone sent you a message?

