especially urgent.

01:10:30.076 --> 01:10:30.966 A:middle
You can have the peace of mind

01:10:30.966 --> 01:10:32.416 A:middle
that you can get contacted and

01:10:32.486 --> 01:10:33.796 A:middle
they can reply urgent and that

01:10:33.796 --> 01:10:35.176 A:middle
message will go through.

01:10:35.356 --> 01:10:36.266 A:middle
We think this is going to be a

01:10:36.266 --> 01:10:38.256 A:middle
real important step in safety in

01:10:38.256 --> 01:10:38.586 A:middle
the car.

