Did you remember back the first

01:17:26.656 --> 01:17:27.846 A:middle
time you started downloading

01:17:27.846 --> 01:17:29.806 A:middle
apps when you use the App Store

01:17:29.926 --> 01:17:31.406 A:middle
and it was so much fun to go in

01:17:31.406 --> 01:17:33.126 A:middle
every single day and discover

01:17:33.126 --> 01:17:34.096 A:middle
the new apps that were

01:17:34.096 --> 01:17:34.566 A:middle
appearing?

01:17:34.566 --> 01:17:36.096 A:middle
I mean, that's an amazing

01:17:36.096 --> 01:17:36.686 A:middle
feeling.

01:17:36.686 --> 01:17:38.146 A:middle
And we're bringing that back

01:17:38.146 --> 01:17:39.956 A:middle
again with this brand new tab

01:17:40.296 --> 01:17:42.406 A:middle
called Today, a whole new way to

01:17:42.406 --> 01:17:43.486 A:middle
discover apps.

01:17:43.706 --> 01:17:44.636 A:middle
It's a place where we can

01:17:44.696 --> 01:17:46.966 A:middle
feature the apps we all love and

