the stories about the developers

01:17:48.966 --> 01:17:49.856 A:middle
who created them.

01:17:49.956 --> 01:17:51.336 A:middle
It's going to be such a great

01:17:51.436 --> 01:17:53.056 A:middle
place for customers to discover

01:17:53.286 --> 01:17:55.046 A:middle
your apps every single day.

