And our team has been hard at

02:03:44.076 --> 02:03:46.516 A:middle
work for many years now on a

02:03:46.516 --> 02:03:48.786 A:middle
breakthrough home speaker.

02:03:50.166 --> 02:03:51.246 A:middle
And it has to do a few things

02:03:51.246 --> 02:03:52.566 A:middle
really great if it's going to be

02:03:52.566 --> 02:03:54.216 A:middle
a great breakthrough speaker.

02:03:55.546 --> 02:03:57.326 A:middle
First, it needs to rock the

02:03:57.326 --> 02:03:58.646 A:middle
house, right?

02:03:59.096 --> 02:04:00.746 A:middle
We need to enjoy our music,

02:04:00.746 --> 02:04:02.706 A:middle
whatever genre you love, really

02:04:02.706 --> 02:04:05.146 A:middle
low or really loud, free from

02:04:05.146 --> 02:04:05.806 A:middle
distortion.

02:04:07.086 --> 02:04:09.916 A:middle
Second, it needs to be spatially

02:04:09.916 --> 02:04:10.856 A:middle
aware.

02:04:11.126 --> 02:04:12.186 A:middle
It's going to fit in different

02:04:12.186 --> 02:04:13.176 A:middle
rooms in our house and it needs

02:04:13.176 --> 02:04:14.306 A:middle
to be smart enough to know what

02:04:14.306 --> 02:04:15.756 A:middle
to do to make the music sound

02:04:15.756 --> 02:04:16.086 A:middle
great.

02:04:17.656 --> 02:04:19.726 A:middle
Third, it has to be really fun

02:04:19.726 --> 02:04:20.186 A:middle
to use.

02:04:20.186 --> 02:04:21.206 A:middle
It has to have a built-in

02:04:21.206 --> 02:04:23.306 A:middle
musicologist, an expert on music

02:04:23.516 --> 02:04:25.026 A:middle
who can help us to hear the

02:04:25.026 --> 02:04:26.706 A:middle
music we love or discover music

02:04:26.706 --> 02:04:27.636 A:middle
we're going to love.

02:04:28.126 --> 02:04:30.466 A:middle
Now we're working on this

02:04:30.466 --> 02:04:32.846 A:middle
speaker for later this year, but

02:04:33.196 --> 02:04:35.016 A:middle
we want to give you, 6000 of our

02:04:35.016 --> 02:04:37.176 A:middle
closest friends, a sneak peek at

02:04:37.176 --> 02:04:38.366 A:middle
it this morning.

02:04:38.766 --> 02:04:41.426 A:middle
And here it is.

